== Headline ==

Database programming with [[Technology:JDBC|JDBC]] and [[Technology:H2|H2-Database]]

Follow this [https://github.com/https://github.com/101companies/101simplejava/tree/master/contributions/simplejdbc link] to the repository.
== Characteristics ==

We use JDBC/SQL for data processing. That is, we use embedded SQL in Java.
== Usage ==
In general see the [https://github.com/101companies/101simplejava/blob/master/contributions/simplejdbc/src/test/java/org/softlang/company/SimpleJdbcTests.java testcase] of this contribution for building and connecting to a H2-Database. 

* Notes:
** Use org.h2.Driver as JDBC driver
** Connecting to a new URL creates automatically a new database:
*** URL for local in-memory database: jdbc:h2:mem:databaseName
*** URL for local not in-memory database: jdbc:h2:path/databaseName
** Use SQL for queries
